1. Bikin database username sama password
    Table
      user
        username: text / char
        password: text / char
  
  Dipake di
    * Login
        masukin username,
        masukin password
        cari ada ga pasangan username dan password yang sama di database
        kalo ada, oke
        kalo engga, exit
      
    * register
        masukin username, password
        cari ada ga username yang sama di database
        kalo ada, skip
        kalo engga, gas (tapi jangan langsung ke beranda dulu)
    
  Mau login / engga (y/n)
    * login -> tampilin login
    * register -> tampilin register